article.headline: Scotty Washington scores 27 to lead Cal State Northridge over Sacramento State 79-69
article.description: — Scotty Washington scored 27 points as Cal State Northridge beat Sacramento State 79-69 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Scotty Washington scores 27 to lead Cal State Northridge over Sacramento State 79-69
article.story: SACRAMENTO, Calif. -- — Scotty Washington scored 27 points as Cal State Northridge beat Sacramento State 79-69 on Saturday night. Washington shot 7 for 13 (4 for 7 from 3-point range) and 9 of 11 from the free-throw line for the Matadors (3-1). Keonte Jones scored 20 points while shooting 7 of 11 from the field and 6 for 6 from the line and added six rebounds. Jacob Holt finished with 20 points for the Hornets (1-3). Julian Vaughns added 14 points and two steals. EJ Neal finished with 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
